                    "cell_text_raw": "Development within the MUR Zone is meant to be of a mixed variety of building forms and Semi-detached or Duplex Dwellings, Single-detached Dwellings, Nursing Homes and Community Care Facilities."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "row_id": "zone-mur-table-21-2-row-2",
                "source_order": 2,
